@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "Nhân viên" as Staff
participant "PaymentPanel\n(View)" as View
participant "BillingController" as Controller
participant "BillingService" as Service
database "MySQL\n(BoardingHouse_DB)" as DB

Note over Staff, DB: QUY TRÌNH THU TIỀN HÓA ĐƠN (TIỀN MẶT / CHUYỂN KHOẢN)

Staff -> View : 1. Chọn hóa đơn cần thu
View -> Controller : 2. confirmPayment(billId, paymentType)
activate Controller

Controller -> Service : 3. processPayment(billId, paymentType)
activate Service

Service -> DB : 4. Begin Transaction
activate DB

' Cập nhật hóa đơn
Service -> DB : 5. UPDATE HOA_DON SET da_thanh_toan = TRUE,\nhinh_thuc_thanh_toan = ?, ngay_thanh_toan = NOW()
DB -->> Service : 6. Success

Service -> DB : 7. Commit
deactivate DB

Service -->> Controller : 8. Payment Processed
deactivate Service

Controller -->> View : 9. Hiển thị thông báo thành công
deactivate Controller

View -->> Staff : 10. In biên lai cho khách
@enduml